query:
INSERT INTO species (name, scientific_name, observed_at, latitude, longitude, geom)
        SELECT $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, ST_SetSRID(ST_MakePoint($5, $4), 4326)
        WHERE NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM species
            WHERE name = $1
            AND scientific_name = $2
            AND observed_at = $3
            AND latitude = $4
            AND longitude = $5
        )
